title: NsvRecorder.1.01.Incl.Keygen-ONY
description:
APPLICATION : NsvRecorder 1.01 Incl Keygen
         OS : Win
       TYPE : Video Recorder
        WWW : http://www.nsvrecorder.com
    RELDATE : no idea
 PROTECTION : Aspack / Serial
 CRKRELDATE : 09/04/2008

INSTALLATION: Install.
              Use keygen to generate your "Site License" serial.

       NOTES: 
              The name function in the keygen has the only purpose
              to make your serial unique to you. You can still register
              NsvRecorder with any name with the generated key.
              Please use chars like a-z and/or numbers. Chars like %_# )]/!
              will work but might be banned in future versions.
              
              Nuff said. Enjoy! / ONY

       ABOUT:
       
              NsvRecorder is an easy-to-use tool that can record streaming Video
              or Audio (nsv or nsa) content from Winamp.com broadcasted through
              HTTP or UNSV protocol. Multiple URLs can be recorded simultaneously.  
              You can capture music video, film video and so on. Save your
              recordings as files on your PC and watch them anytime you like, even
              without an Internet connection.
              
              Main Features:

              * Capture winamp video streaming(http://www.winamp.com/videos/)
              * Category Manager
              * Record Multi video streaming simultaneously
